{"title":"纱厂女工歌","authors":["朱桂芳"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":1,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"纱厂女工歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十五岁女工  朱桂芳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一台细纱车长又长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四百个锭子转的忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姐妹三人来看车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个更比一个强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大姐姐真不错，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一分钟接头十五个；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二姐姐真是行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把车清洁的很干净；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三妹妹手艺巧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十个毛棍看的好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姐妹三个真能干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一心争取当模范，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不跑车，手不闲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车上不把疙疸练。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"络纱的姐妹八个人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身上都束着白围裙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"组长一吹络纱哨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八个姐妹都来到。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"组长急忙摇下车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姐妹们一排排络起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只听纱管乒乓响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落得好象闪电快。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四百个穗子四百个管，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十秒钟就络完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车把一搬开了车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八个姐妹都上线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心又灵来手又巧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不到半分钟都上好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姐妹们飞跑把纱倒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倒到口袋里又去络。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"络纱的，真积极，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"络完纱了不休息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又到车上去接头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看车的姐妹笑嘻嘻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗插在车头上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旗子飘飘真好看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家看见了真眼气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"努力加油把活干。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当模范，真光荣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"名字都在报上登，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万人儿都看报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都说我们生产好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争模范，多生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多多生产支援前线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早早打垮将介石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全国工人把身翻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建设新民主主义新中国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家美满的过太平年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（转载自石家庄日报）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}